    <body>
        <h1>보드게임 SET</h1>
        <div id="system-message"></div>
        <div id="button-wrapper">
            <button id="reset">새 게임 시작</button>
            <div id="deck">
                <div class="card-small card-small-1">
                </div>
                <div class="card-small card-small-2">
                </div>
                <div class="card-small card-small-3">
                </div>
                <div class="card-small card-small-4" id="top-card">
                    (0장)
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="scoreboard-wrapper">
            <p id="scoreboard-head">점수</p>
            <div id="scoreboard"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="board"></div>
        <div id="interactions">
            <ul id="messages"></ul>
            <form action="#" id="msg-form">
                <label>메시지 입력</label>
                <div id="message-input-wrapper">
                    <input type="text" name="lname" id="msg-box">
                    <input type="submit" id="msg-submit" value="전송">
                </div>
            </form>
            <br />
            <h2>메시지 목록</h2>
            <ul id="msg-list"></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="modal micromodal-slide" id="reset-modal" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal__overlay" tabindex="-1" data-micromodal-close>
                <div class="modal__container" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="reset-modal-title">
                    <header class="modal__header">
                        <h2 class="modal__title" id="reset-modal-title">
                            새 게임 시작
                        </h2>
                        <button class="modal__close close-modal" aria-label="창 닫기"></button>
                    </header>
                    <div class="modal__content" id="reset-modal-content">
                        <p>
                            아직 게임이 진행중입니다. 정말로 현재 게임을 종료하고 새 게임을 시작하시겠습니까?
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <footer class="modal__footer">
                        <button class="modal__btn" id="reset-confirm-button" aria-label="새 게임 시작">새 게임 시작</button>
                        <button class="modal__btn modal__btn-primary close-modal" aria-label="창 닫기">창 닫기</button>
                    </footer>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/socket.io/2.0.4/socket.io.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/js-cookie/2.1.3/js.cookie.min.js"></script>
